myData.title: Gupchup
myData.description: Gupchup, the most renowned food of the state famously known as Golgoppa or panipuri accross India . In the South, its Panipuri or Gapchup presented with Onion and Pudina water and in the East generally in Odisha, Bihar, Jharkhand, and West Bengal its Gupchup.
